subNode:value.scalar:string: The "Only account creation" registration option allows the customer to register faster, and create his/her address later.
If you chose yes, your customer will have to provide at least one phone number to register.
After customer logs in, you can recall and display the content of his/her last shopping cart.
Send an email with summary account (email, password) after registration.
Minimum time required to regenerate a password.
Activate or deactivate B2B mode. When this option is enabled, B2B features will be made available.
